            . I am the wife of 
               <persName id="t18320517-270-person1967">
                  George 
                  Simpson
               <interp inst="t18320517-270-person1967" type="surname" value="Simpson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320517-270-person1967" type="given" value="George"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320517-270-person1967" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have the care of Harriet Sulman - I put the necklace on her neck about three o'clock, and saw it safe about five minutes before I heard her cry out; I ran to the door, and saw my husband run after the boy - her father's name is John Sulman.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183205170123"></xptr>JAMES BLACK (Police-constable S 208). I took the prisoner in charge.</p>
